comments: Gasol (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Mills (SAS).
Lowry (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball during rebounding with Gasol (TOR).
Powell (TOR) maintains a bent forearm to DeRozan's (SAS) side during his driving shot.
Lowry (TOR) and White (SAS) briefly engage and disengage while the shot is going through the basket.
Gasol (TOR) establishes a legal position in White's (SAS) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
VanVleet (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot by DeRozan (SAS).
VanVleet (TOR) establishes a legal position in White's (SAS) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Siakam's (TOR) left arm is not vertical and makes contact with Walker IV's (SAS) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
White (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Siakam (TOR) at the end of the drive.
Lowry (TOR) makes contact with the ball to dislodge it from Murray (SAS) before making marginal contact with his body as the ball is going out of bounds.
White (SAS) commits a take foul on VanVleet (TOR).
Powell (TOR) makes marginal contact with DeRozan (SAS) during the inbound.
Aldridge (SAS) establishes a legal position in Lowry's (TOR) path and firms up on his right leg during the screen.
Ibaka (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Belinelli (SAS).

Powell (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Belinelli (SAS) and the two players make incidental leg to leg contact after the shot is released and Belinelli has landed.
